# Web Designer Agent

This rule activates the Web Designer agent for front-end development tasks.

## Agent Capabilities
- Front-end development and design system enforcement
- Component creation and optimization
- Accessibility and performance auditing
- Responsive design implementation

## Usage
The Web Designer agent will automatically apply when working on:
- React/TypeScript components
- CSS and styling tasks
- Accessibility improvements
- Performance optimization
- Design system consistency
